{"tid":1206534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(民陣麻煩入入嚟)其實應該畀個死線政府","createTime":"2019-06-12T03:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T05:07:00.000Z","uid":129013,"like":117,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca94ee9406242aef0ed70f9b9af64f172ba293f","tid":1206534,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"過左今日，聽日已經好難再有咁嘅民氣，所以有需要速戰速決。<br />\n<br />\n其實依家係差緊一個最最最決定性嘅理由去推翻惡法，所以要兇鳩佢，話佢知今日之內必須取消惡法，否則就有一堆佢接受唔到嘅條件。<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n1.以全體泛民立法會議員發聲明，要求美國取消香港關係法<br />\n2.以全體泛民立法會議員發聲明，香港將不再適合外資經商<br />\n3.以全體泛民立法會議員發聲明，要求全世界國家取消香港免簽證待遇<br />\n4.不再指揮今次運動，任由年輕人自己發揮<br />\n<br />\n以上只係我諗到嘅少少意見，我知各位充滿智慧嘅連登巴打有更好嘅計仔，麻煩屌細力d"},{"pid":"7db6e38d12349c1d37ad90502453f49c4d1354a7","tid":1206534,"uid":117983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:25:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"799fb5b7ebda152e2be6f7995fe52fd4e1da6da0","tid":1206534,"uid":117983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"413510f07cd04d57f40e7f6f0e304fa8ada4f323","tid":1206534,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:26:42.000Z","msg":"民陣做嘢啦 人就喺度喇"},{"pid":"a809507569331f89a6cfb71af8cd09afba05fbff","tid":1206534,"uid":241723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:29:58.000Z","msg":"同意 有左死線又可以統一戰力 等要衝個班可以一齊衝"},{"pid":"5a2deb004886f14e9211a0ea39551f4738fcd5e9","tid":1206534,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:30:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e826bee90a7ff748d4cdfa0b39f74e5e680dc4cf","tid":1206534,"uid":94781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b00154094e23f59edf9b2a192e5acc85c0d6004b","tid":1206534,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"推到民陣見到"},{"pid":"9a5d173001ac0b542cbedf51f08fba295df880c5","tid":1206534,"uid